**Coyote Pup** | Werewolf Group
__Basics__
The Coyote Pup and other coyotes share a secret channel, however they do not know the other wolves
__Details__
The Coyote Pup knows the identity of the other coyotes and can communicate with them
The Coyote Pup is not a lycan, nor are they a member of the wolfpack.
When the last original Greater Coyote dies, the coyote's channel is disbanded and the Coyote Pup joins the wolfpack instead.

__Simplified__
The Coyote Pup is a packless lycanless wolf who is part of a group of other coyotes, should the Greater Coyote die the Coyote Pup joins the wolfpack instead
